hington, and collecting signatures at energized events like the March for Our Lives, Keep Families Together rallies, and Pride events across the state. Lows included the loss of a founder and beloved Chair Kathy Angel to cancer in the last few weeks of the campaign.\n\nThe campaign did not use paid-signature gatherers and had no paid staff. Even the volunteer campaign director collected signatures, easily 1000 alone.\n\nWhole Washington wants to hear your ideas for moving forward and pushing further. We will be planning an event shortly. Stay tuned!";s:20:"text_selected_editor";s:4:"html";s:5:"autop";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:32:"12220644425b62284355780868493495";s:19:"_sow_form_timestamp";s:13:"1533164880101";s:11:"panels_info";a:7:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:2;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:2;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"307267f1-433f-4a8c-8e66-b759eb3d31f1";s:5:"style";a:3:{s:5:"class";s:31:"homepage-section maxwidth-800px";s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";}}}i:3;a:15:{s:5:"image";i:246;s:14:"image_fallback";s:0:"";s:4:"size";s:4:"full";s:5:"align";s:6:"center";s:11:"title_align";s:7:"default";s:5:"title";s:15:"horizontal rule";s:14:"title_position";s:6:"hidden";s:3:"alt";s:0:"";s:3:"url";s:0:"";s:5:"bound";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:31:"5972159745bb70ea506061399260431";s:19:"_sow_form_timestamp";s:0:"";s:11:"panels_info";a:6:{s:5:"class";s:30:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget";s:4:"grid";i:3;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:3;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"89d0b9cb-0aff-4e76-8b12-936c2e78e2f3";s:5:"style";a:3:{s:5:"class";s:15:"horizontal-rule";s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";}}s:10:"new_window";b:0;s:10:"full_width";b:0;}i:4;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:76:"<h2>We want everyone to have high‑quality, comprehensive healthcare.</h2>\n";s:20:"text_selected_editor";s:4:"tmce";s:5:"autop";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:31:"3874738365b64ca83b30de419983347";s:1