 (350, 83, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:6:"filter";s:1:"1";s:4:"text";s:5503:"<div id="intro" class="intro"><div class="text-content"><h2><strong>I-1600 Literature</strong></h2><p><em>Printable materials to help with signature gathering and spreading the word</em></p><p> <a title="Quarter Sheets" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1525470512/I1600QuarterSheetNewest.pdf?1525470512" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Quarter Sheets</a> <strong>The Benefits &amp; </strong><strong>Things You Can Do Now</strong></p><ul><li>Great for handouts</li></ul><p><a title="The Benefits and Financial Contributions" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1524797436/HalfSheetI1600Informed2Up.pdf?1524797436" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Half Sheet</a> <strong>The Benefits and Financial Contributions</strong></p><ul><li>Print it out doubled-sided and cut in half. Shows calculations for revenue sources.</li></ul><p><a title="FAQs, Benefits, Financial Contributions" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1525891203/Yes1600_FAQ_EN.pdf?1525891203" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FAQs 2.0</a></p><ul><li>Also includes Benefits and Financial Contributions</li><li><a href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1525719798/Yes1600_FAQ_SP_page1.pdf?1525719798" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FAQs in Spanish</a></li></ul><p><a title="I\'m a Volunteer - Sign My Petition" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/12FPBSbCMbG5cCFQxwiAMMgLJP0pCr82ZExnj6raSplc/edit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Petition Board Backer</a></p><ul><li>Print and tape to the back of your board. Let people know you\'re a volunteer and what you want them to sign</li></ul><p><a title="Savings for Residents, Providers, Businesses" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1524795049/BizLit.pdf?1524795049" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Business Literature</a></p><ul><li>Savings for Residents, Providers, and Businesses. With FAQs</li></ul><p><a title="Pay/Save/Benefit" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1528640736/PaySaveBenefits.pdf?1528640736" target="_blank" rel="noopener">How do we Pay / What do we Save / What are the Benefits</a></p><ul><li>Great visual guide to have on hand while out gathering signatures. It helps explain the funding mechanisms and savings.</li></ul><p><a title="Business Stand up" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1528638756/Business_Stand_Up.jpg?1528638756" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Local Business - Petition Host Board</a></p><ul><li>11 x 14. Benefits and signing instructions. Adhere to foam core or 1/2 yard sign with stand up piece on back. </li></ul><p><a title="Printable Credo" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1524790711/Yes1600Credo.pdf?1524790711" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Yes on I-1600 Credo</a></p><ul><li>Remember why we\'re doing this. We want to change the world!</li></ul><h2><strong>I-1600 Resources</strong></h2><p><em>In-depth information about the initiative</em></p><p><a href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1520793978/Initiative_1600_-_Full_Text.pdf?1520793978" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Full Text of the I-1600 Initiative</a></p><p><a title="Executive Summary of Financial Analysis" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1522283164/WW-fiscalstudy-executive-summary.docx.pdf?1522283164" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Executive Summary of Financial Analysis by Dr. Gerald Friedman</a> (17 pages)</p><p><a title="Full Economic Analysis by Dr. Friedman" href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/266/attachments/original/1522282388/Economic_Analysis_of_Single_Payer_Health_Care_in__Washington_State__180220_%281%29.pdf?1522282388" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Full Economic Analysis by Dr. Gerald Friedman</a> (63 pages)</p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AT1GLTHMQeg&amp;feature=youtu.be">Dr. Gerald Friedman\'s Lecture in Shoreline</a> (video)</p><p><a href="https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/wholewashington/pages/176/attachments/original/1520734355/Dr._Gerald_Friedman\'s_Presentation.pptx?1520734355">Companion Presentation to Dr. Friedman\'s Lecture</a> (slides)</p><p> </p><h2><strong>Single Payer / Universal Healthcare Resources</strong></h2><p><em>Learn more about the concept of Single Payer healthcare systems in general</em></p><p><strong>Great for house-parties and fundraisers:</strong></p><p><a href="https://fixithealthcare.com/watch-the-movie/">Fix It: Healthcare at the Tipping Point</a></p><ul><li>Approximately 60 minutes. Free</li></ul><p><a href="http://nowisthetimemovie.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Now is the Time: Healthcare for Everybody</a></p><ul><li>70 or 35 minute versions. Pay Per View $4.99 / Download for $20 </li></ul><p><a title="More resources available for talking to specific groups" href="http://healthoverprofit.org/convince-me-tools-for-various-constituencies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Convince Me Tools</a></p><ul><li>Online resource with helpful info for talking to specific groups, like Businesses, Conservatives, Democrats, Healthcare Professionals, the general public, etc. </li></ul></div></div>";s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";s:11:"panels_info";a:7:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:0;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"87cf6a91-3505-467a-83a0-0f2a8a204877";s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}}s:5:"grids";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}s:10:"grid_cells";a:1:{i:0;a:4:{s:4:"grid";i:0;s:5:"index";i:0;s:6:"weight";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}}'),
