 (73, 1, '2018-08-20 19:10:00', '2018-08-20 19:10:00', '<div id="pl-50"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-50-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style" ><div id="pgc-50-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-50-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" ><div class="so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base">\n<div class="siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget">\n	<h2>What\'s Included</h2><p>By passing I-1600, Washington State will transform the healthcare system and residents\' lives.</p><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-66" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Benefits.png" alt="benefits chart" width="502" height="601" /></p><h3>Benefits also include:</h3><ul><li>Hearing aids</li><li>Physical and occupational therapy</li><li>Palliative, Hospice, end-of-life care</li><li>Acupuncture, some massage and other healing therapies</li></ul><h3>Who\'s Included</h3><p>Everyone’s in. No one’s out. If you’re a Washington State resident, the Whole Washington Trust will cover you.</p><ul><li>Children up to the age of 19 are included with no premiums.</li><li>The unemployed are included.</li><li>The homeless are included.</li><li>Those traveling temporarily out of the state are included.</li><li>Those living here for a temporary job are included.</li></ul></div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>', 'Benefits', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-20 19:10:00', '2018-08-20 19:10:00', '', 50, 'http://localhost/2018/08/20/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
