 (141, 1, '2018-08-23 19:52:37', '2018-08-23 19:52:37', '<div class="left-column">\r\n<div class="content-pages-show-basic">\r\n<div id="content">\r\n<div id="intro" class="intro">\r\n<div class="text-content">\r\n\r\nGathering with other local signature gatherers is a great way to get going and keep up your momentum. You can share tips, buddy up, and plan coverage for events or locations. We have some active groups that meet regularly and are doing amazing work. If there\'s one close to you, ask to join in.*\r\n\r\n<a title="Pierce County Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/universalhealthcare.piercecounty/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">I-1600 <strong>Pierce County</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Thurston County Facebook Group " href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/144959426325096/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">I-1600 Whole Washington <strong>Thurston County</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<strong><a title="Whatcom County Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1831987327074221/?fref=gc&amp;dti=151585728745908&amp;hc_location=ufi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Whatcom </a></strong><a title="Whatcom County Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1831987327074221/?fref=gc&amp;dti=151585728745908&amp;hc_location=ufi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YES on I-1600!</a>\r\n\r\n<a title="WWU Facebook Group" href="https://m.facebook.com/groups/992217574261148" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>WWU</strong> YES on I-1600!</a>\r\n\r\n<a title="South King County FB Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/384793505367874/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>South King County</strong> for I-1600</a> (Burien, SeaTac, Renton, Des Moines, Federal Way, Tukwila)\r\n\r\n<a title="Bothell, Kenmore, LFP Local Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/220204991867217/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600/<strong>Bothell, Kenmore, Lake Forest Park</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Capitol Hill Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/632333843780136/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600<strong> Capitol Hill</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="CD 3 Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/2000343443328466/?fref=gc&amp;dti=151585728745908&amp;hc_location=ufi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600 - <strong>CD3</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Eastside Local Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1771729916216354/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600 - <strong>Eastside</strong></a> (of Seattle)\r\n\r\n<a title="Spokane Facebook Group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/605118103153900/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600 - <strong>Spokane</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="West Seattle, South Park, Georgetown local group" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1596118490506079/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yes on 1600 - <strong>West Seattle, South Park, Georgetown</strong></a>\r\n\r\nIf there\'s no current group in your area, start your own! Create a Facebook Group and reach out to <a href="mailto:georgia@wholewashington.org">georgia@wholewashington.org</a>. We\'ll look for other active volunteers nearby and can get you literature and supplies.\r\n\r\n*These groups are run by volunteers. The comments and posts in these groups and pages do not necessarily reflect the position of the Whole Washington organization.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Find a Local Group', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'find-a-local-group', '', '', '2018-08-24 22:44:28', '2018-08-24 22:44:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?page_id=141', 0, 'page', '', 0),
