 (200, 1, '2018-08-24 22:39:03', '2018-08-24 22:39:03', 'Farmers Markets are great places to volunteer to get signatures OR to find volunteers if you want to sign.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Farmers Market</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Where</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>When</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Details</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a title="Auburn Farmers Market" href="http://www.auburnfarmersmarket.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Auburn</a></td>\r\n<td>1140 Auburn Way South</td>\r\n<td>Sundays 10-3</td>\r\n<td>Les Grove Park</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.sfmamarkets.com/visit-ballard-farmers-market" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ballard</a></td>\r\n<td>NW Market Street and 22nd Ave, Seattle</td>\r\n<td>Sundays 10-3</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.bellinghamfarmers.org/about-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bellingham</a></td>\r\n<td>On sidewalk outside of market</td>\r\n<td>Wednesdays 3-7</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://www.countryvillagebothell.com/bothell-farmers-market" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bothell</a></td>\r\n<td>Bothell Country Village</td>\r\n<td>Fridays 12-6</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="https://www.discoverburien.org/farmers-market/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Burien</a></td>\r\n<td>Burien Town Square Park</td>\r\n<td>Thursdays 11-6</td>\r\n<td width="419">Will share a table with volunteer group-Contact Georgia for more info georgia@wholewashington.org</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a title="Cap Hill Farmers Market" href="https://seattlefarmersmarkets.org/markets/broadway" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Capitol Hill</a></td>\r\n<td>Broadway Ave E and E Pine Str</td>\r\n<td>Sundays 11-3</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a title="Columbia City Farmers Market" href="https://seattlefarmersmarkets.org/markets/columbia-city" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Columbia City</a></td>\r\n<td>37th Ave S &amp; S 